    <p class="lead mt-3">
      <strong>PneumoCare</strong> is a smart and lightweight pneumonia detection web application built using 
      <strong>Node.js, Express, MySQL, HTML, CSS,</strong> and <strong>JavaScript.</strong>  
      It helps healthcare professionals and lab technicians detect pneumonia early using lab parameters such as 
      <strong>WBC Count, Neutrophil Percentage, CRP Level,</strong> and <strong>Oxygen Level.</strong>
    </p>

